{
  "stem": "2067.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I ask her whether I could accompany her, which I believe reluctantly she accepted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, on-- on the way home, which took about 10 minutes or so, 15 minutes walk perhaps, I tried to impress her by telling her of my experiences in Spain and the languages and the travels that I had done, and all kind of stuff that didn't interest her in the least.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when I finally said goodnight to her and left, I thought, that was it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'll never see her again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shortly afterwards, maybe a couple of weeks later, I got a telephone call from my same friend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, we are planning to have a New Year's Eve party, only we don't know where.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, I noticed you were quite interested in [INAUDIBLE] Parfumier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, how do you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, an idiot could have noticed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you be willing to have the party in your apartment?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, by all means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when I had the chance to call her and invite her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That brought us a little closer, but still no friendship yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, 1940 came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in April, I got a call again from my friend or he told me, he said, Maccabi, is now starting the tennis, to prepare the tennis season.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since you are member, why don't you-- why don't you join to tennis club?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did when he said that [INAUDIBLE] Parfumier is for years already a member there and is a very good tennis player.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also played tennis, but not as well as she did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's where I met then my future wife.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We became friendly and started dating.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
